headline: Jennifer Kupcho Clinches $1 Million Aon Risk Reward Challenge Title in Final-Event Comeback
summary: Aon plc (NYSE: AON), a leading global professional services firm, and the LPGA Tour today announced Jennifer Kupcho as the winner of the 2025 Aon Risk Reward Challenge, securing the title in dramatic fashion during the final event of the regular season. Kupcho delivered a remarkable late-season push — highlighted by a pivotal birdie and eagle on the par-5 14th at The ANNIKA — to overtake the field and claim the $1 million prize and Aon Trophy.
